	<li id="lb69a047_r"><a href="http://hdl.loc.gov/loc.music/lbphotos.69a047">Bernstein with Felicia, Jamie, Alexander, and Nina on rooftop with New York skyline</a>. &copy; Made available online with permission of photographer, Don Hunstein.</li>
